Dear Sir/Madam,

Thank you for registering for the Online Round Table about LNG in Bulgaria 2020 and Beyond: New Opportunities for Diversification, Security and Trade - December 10th, 2020.

This is an invitations only event. You will be notified and will receive a link for access.

For further information please mail: events@amcham.bg  <mailto:events@amcham.bg> 

Best regards,

The American Chamber of Commerce in Bulgaria
